data.description: Beautifully updated home on a 1.1 acre lot, located in a cul-de-sac.  New roof in 2022, furnace/AC in 2018, siding in 2019, fresh paint and flooring!  Compliant septic and an additional 24x24 garage out back!  Huge master in lower level with electric fireplace and walk in closet.  Cedar Lake voluntary association of $150/year to use the 7 acre park nearby.  Within 1 mile of park, town and 1/2 mile from the public access.  This one owner home is in pristine condition.  Move right in to this updated home and enjoy!  ****$2,000 buyer credit for rate buy down!****
